OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA weakening
OL,6,Fband of cloud and patchy rain
OL,7,Fcontinuing to move southeastwards
OL,8,Ftonight, with clear spells either
OL,9,Fside. Some blustery showers affecting
OL,10,Fthe far north, with a patchy rural air
OL,11,Ffrost developing under the clearer
OL,12,Fskies.
OL,13,
OL,14,CMonday:FA chilly start with some
OL,15,Fsunshine, especially in the south.
OL,16,FCloud will thicken in the north as a
OL,17,Fband of rain and strong winds moves
OL,18,Finto Scotland and Northern Ireland.
